  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MineSweeper.R is a roguelike Minesweeper game inspired by Noita’s spell-programming system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your skill sequences—one click can trigger a massive chain of abilities and wipe out huge minefields in a single move!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>Attention!!!: This game requires some prior knowledge of Minesweeper. Players who do not know Minesweeper should purchase with caution!</u></i></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combine freely. Infinite possibilities.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ skill glyphs, up to 9 skill slots, and fully customizable trigger sequences—ignite infinite possibilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/527bc93d4c383919671ccc7e15f4774e.poster.avif?t=1774096361\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/527bc93d4c383919671ccc7e15f4774e.webm?t=1774096361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/527bc93d4c383919671ccc7e15f4774e.mp4?t=1774096361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Integration and Upgrade, Skill Creation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Digital data and skills are combined to increase the number and scope of skills; skills are merged to generate new skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/78c0cafc5fb30b32bcd73ebd66831871.poster.avif?t=1774096361\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/78c0cafc5fb30b32bcd73ebd66831871.webm?t=1774096361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/78c0cafc5fb30b32bcd73ebd66831871.mp4?t=1774096361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meta progression for effortless growth.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multi-path meta progression makes Minesweeper smoother and lets you build even stronger skill sequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/498fbb5a968bf4b18c25885a58a83677.poster.avif?t=1774096361\" width=328 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/498fbb5a968bf4b18c25885a58a83677.webm?t=1774096361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/498fbb5a968bf4b18c25885a58a83677.mp4?t=1774096361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MineSweeper.R is a roguelike Minesweeper game inspired by Noita’s spell-programming system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your skill sequences—one click can trigger a massive chain of abilities and wipe out huge minefields in a single move!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>Attention!!!: This game requires some prior knowledge of Minesweeper. Players who do not know Minesweeper should purchase with caution!</u></i></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combine freely. Infinite possibilities.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ skill glyphs, up to 9 skill slots, and fully customizable trigger sequences—ignite infinite possibilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/527bc93d4c383919671ccc7e15f4774e.poster.avif?t=1774096361\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/527bc93d4c383919671ccc7e15f4774e.webm?t=1774096361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/527bc93d4c383919671ccc7e15f4774e.mp4?t=1774096361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Integration and Upgrade, Skill Creation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Digital data and skills are combined to increase the number and scope of skills; skills are merged to generate new skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4368600/extras/78c0cafc5fb30b32bcd73ebd66831871.poster.avif?t=1774096361\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.